name: ORO II: Arc de Triomphe under a full moon
description: ORO II is the second installment of the ORO series, a set of 3D renders made in Blender that revolve around gold. Enjoy the splendor and beauty of this golden version of the Arc de Triomphe.  This work, "ORO II: Arc de Triomphe under a full moon", makes use of the 3d model https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/arc-de-triomphe-paris-with-texture-f5096afb1a3345e2bf1a82231d9f89c4 by https://sketchfab.com/HoangHiepVu , used under https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
